ngue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話就話混浴，個場有女性專用池，所以都係男有男浸、女有女浸</blockquote><br />\n好似幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係長假期、暑假<br />\n伊豆遊客唔多好舒服，個氣氛好悠閒<br />\n<br />\n係距離東京遠少少，好在特急一程直達</blockquote><br />\n上次睇河津櫻<br />\n全部日本人咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8297e087d86f0c8364055c13f81f678bcd352909","tid":267570,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"一個人唔去飛田新地 不如唔好去大阪<br />\n唔入都要去行下<br />\nd 日本人都好似年宵咁行<br />\n包你大開眼界"},{"pid":"714f30536877687f4e6a40f080fc8ae69d3a8377","tid":267570,"uid":24112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個人唔去飛田新地 不如唔好去大阪<br />\n唔入都要去行下<br />\nd 日本人都好似年宵咁行<br />\n包你大開眼界</blockquote><br />\n冇話一定去大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4d1805bb55bf58a350bbce3be0084390eaf772","tid":267570,"uid":24112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812d4a6a9b76f72f0affd7d86fb5039682cca5d9","tid":267570,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"有冇地方多星、有雪山、有得浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c3dabe59bc9e1d9280007133c945c1884ae049","tid":267570,"uid":24112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇地方多星、有雪山、有得浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雪山 夏天未有丫?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373585d3523327f4d53ba0d3e97381e5d6e14be6","tid":267570,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T14:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇地方多星、有雪山、有得浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.